perly deselected after termination. I'm working on the data synchronization and UI updates based on the API response.\n\n\n**Refactoring Assignment Functions**\n\nI'm now refactoring `handleTerminateAgent`. I'm focusing on refining its error handling and also, ensuring proper state updates after the API call, and adding logs. I've also re-examined `handleAssignOwner`, finding its implementation to be quite clean and effective within the current API structure. I'm checking how the `agents` state block is written to ensure consistency.\n\n\n"}}
