{"ts":"2026-06-27T18:09:46.007Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"submit_and_exit","toolCallId":"l4hdkuou","input":{"summary":"Successfully connected both the Admin Projects and AI Operations dashboard interfaces to active, secure REST backend CRUD APIs in app/admin/projects/page.tsx and app/admin/ai-operations/page.tsx.\n\n### Implementation Summary:\n1. **Bearer Token Auto-Synchronization (`lib/api-client.ts`):** \n   Integrated an automatic JWT synchronization layer (`ensureValidToken()`) that intercepts outbound client-side API requests. If a simulated session is selected via the Preview Switcher, the helper automatically negotiates a secure administrative JWT from the `/api/v1/auth/login` endpoint behind the scenes. This guarantees that CRUD fetch operations always execute with authentic and correctly scoped clearance headers.\n   \n2. **Admin Projects CRUD Integration (`app/admin/projects/page.tsx`):**\n   - Wired up list, filter, create, edit, and deprovision actions to the corresponding `/api/v1/projects` endpoints.\n   - Preserved all Phase 4 desktop table grid alignments and mobile card grids.\n   - Wrapped the entire content panel with premium, responsive **Loading** (pulsing telemetry tunnel indicator) and **Error** (retry handshake warning console) templates, alongside the standard **Empty** state fallback.\n   \n3. **AI Operations Command Center CRUD Integration (`app/admin/ai-operations/page.tsx`):**\n   - Transformed the static preview array into a reactive `useEffect` mount flow syncing with `/api/v1/ai-operations`.\n   - Mapped backend operations properties (`status`, `health`, `agent_type`, `governance_status`) to the premium Phase 4 telemetry visualizations (cores, latency, CPU utilization indices, uptime logs).\n   - Designed and integrated custom \"+ Register Operational Agent\" and \"Edit Operational Agent\" Modals, allowing fully functional creation, parameter tuning, assignee handshakes, a